		<td class="thead" colspan="2">Advanced Thread Linking</td>
	</tr>
	<tr valign="top">
		<td class="alt2" width="175"><b>Description:</b></td>
		<td class="alt2">The [thread] tag allows you to link to threads by specifying the threadid.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr valign="top">
		<td class="alt1" width="175"><b>Usage:</b></td>
		<td class="alt1">[thread=<i>(thread ID)</i>]<i>(link text)</i>[/thread]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr valign="top">
		<td class="alt2" width="175"><b>Example Usage:</b></td>
